latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY Face Mask for acne prone skin
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ingredients :- 
Honey - tspoon
Cinnamon powder (dalchini) - half tspoon
Lemon - half cut squeezed 
Apply for 8-10 mins and rinse with cold water can do this 2 times in a week or even ones a week. 
Honey used by me @vedaaz_organics 
Check them out for great organic products.
